Samsung Electronics Nigeria has said it is celebrating women in Nigeria in its Samsung Mother’s Day offer. In a statement, the company said, “Samsung appliances are an epitome of strength, reliability and consistency and we can liken Mothers’ similarly as the symbol of the same standard. At Samsung we believe that mothers must be celebrated so in light of this, we would be giving out gifts to our deserving mothers.” According to the company, the first 300 people to buy any Samsung home appliances from its authorised stores between March 13th 2023 and  March 31st, 2023 will get amazing prizes, adding that there will be free delivery and installation in Abuja and Lagos. The statement added, ‘The company inspires the world and shapes the future with transformative ideas and technologies, redefining the worlds of TVs, smartphones, wearable devices, tablets, cameras, digital appliances, printers, medical equipment, network systems and semiconductor and LED solutions.”